sequenceDiagram
    participant M as Broker Master
    participant S as Broker Replica
    participant C as Controller Raft Group
    participant N as NameServer
    participant CL as Client/Proxy

    M->>C: 心跳与副本状态
    S->>C: 心跳与复制进度
    M--xC: Master 故障
    C->>C: 判断多数派与候选副本
    C->>S: 选举为新 Master
    S->>N: 注册新的 Master 路由
    CL->>N: 刷新路由
    CL->>S: 恢复发送和消费
